lenders.name: Prakash
lenders.loan_because: Mary was an older woman with 12 children, which could potentially mean she has more hands for help, but also means here are many mouths to feed. That led me to choose her.

lenders.name: Samantha
lenders.loan_because: I choose borrowers based on the effect their business might have on others, my personal interests, and where I live. I also want to see that the business has a clear goal for the funds they seek.
